description: "Lights in a jar" is my first NFT, there is a reason why I chose this to be my first one, I'm a long time crypto skeptic, this is an economic and a personal belief experiment. The lights represent my creativity encapsulated in a three-dimensional glass maze which they perpetually navigate but cannot escape. Buy the NFT to make me believe in the crypto art scene, I will not mint another NFT until someone buys this one, you will have the honor to "break" the jar and free the lights.
